OL,3,C'I've seen Dad cry for first time':
OL,4,COutpour of support in fight to be
OL,5,CBritish
OL,7,Fto help with the legal challenge has
OL,8,Fnow reached more than #32,000.
OL,10,FNelson said he was overwhelmed by the
OL,11,Fsupport.
OL,13,F"I am very grateful to all the people
OL,14,F- both people who donated money and
OL,15,Fpeople who sent words of comfort," he
OL,16,Fsaid.
OL,18,F"It shows me and my family that we are
OL,19,Fnot alone."
