OL,3,C'I've seen Dad cry for first time':
OL,4,COutpour of support in fight to be
OL,5,CBritish
OL,7,FThe dad assumed he was a citizen for
OL,8,Fmany years but when he applied for a
OL,9,Fpassport in 2019 he was told he had no
OL,10,Fright to be in the UK.
OL,12,FInstead the Home Office told him he
OL,13,Fwould need to apply for the 10-year
OL,14,Froute to settlement, which would cost
OL,15,Faround #7,000.
OL,17,FNelson's son Jacob said the family
OL,18,Fhopes the outpouring of public support
OL,19,Fmay influence the Home Office.
