OL,3,C'I've seen Dad cry for first time':
OL,4,COutpour of support in fight to be
OL,5,CBritish
OL,7,FHe revealed they had received one
OL,8,Fanonymous donation of #5,000 but that
OL,9,Fthe main objective was to spread the
OL,10,Fword out about "the injustice."
OL,12,F"Thank you to everyone," he said.
OL,14,F"My dad never shows his emotions. I
OL,15,Fthink I've seen him cry for the first
OL,16,Ftime in the 26 years I've been alive."
OL,18,FThe family say that the money will go
OL,19,Fto charity if Mr Shardey wins his case
OL,20,Fand has no legal costs to pay.
